S9E1.title: The One After I Do
S9E1.des:
Monica and Chandler's wedding reception is
                almost upstaged by the news that Rachel is pregnant.

S9E2.title: The One with the Red Sweater
S9E2.des:
As they prepare to leave the wedding hotel, an
                excited Monica and Phoebe speculate about who might be the father of pregnant Rachel's baby.

S9E3.title: The One Where Rachel Tells ...
S9E3.des:
Everyone seems to know who the father of
                Rachel's unborn baby is except for the man himself: Ross.

S9E4.title: The One with the Videotape
S9E4.des:
Ross and Rachel try to explain how they ended up
                in bed together six weeks earlier, but the conversation quickly devolves into an argument.

S9E5.title: The One with Rachel's Date
S9E5.des:
Ross is horrified to learn that Rachel is going
                on a date with a handsome actor, especially since she is pregnant with Ross' child.

S9E6.title: The One with the Halloween Party
S9E6.des:
At Monica's Halloween party, Phoebe becomes
                attracted to Eric, the friendly fiancé of her flighty twin, Ursula.

S9E7.title: The One with the Stain
S9E7.des:
Ross is happy to learn that pregnant Rachel
                wants to find her own apartment. Phoebe is ecstatic that Eric has chosen her over her twin sister,
                Ursula.

S9E8.title: The One with the Stripper
S9E8.des:
Rachel nervously tells her short-tempered father
                that she is pregnant with Ross' baby. Monica feels guilty for denying Chandler a bachelor party.

S9E9.title: The One with the Rumor
S9E9.des:
Monica invites Will, her high school friend,
                over for Thanksgiving dinner -- unaware that he isn't too fond of Rachel.

S9E10.title: The One with Monica's Boots
S9E10.des:
Chandler becomes upset when Monica spends a
                fortune on a luxurious pair of black boots. Phoebe tries to meet Sting.

S9E11.title: The One with the Creepy Holiday Card
S9E11.des:
Ross becomes nervous when his new girlfriend,
                Mona, wants to mail cute Christmas cards with both of their pictures on it.

S9E12.title: The One Where Joey Dates Rachel
S9E12.des:
In order to prepare Joey for his big date the
                following night, Rachel eagerly agrees to accompany him for an evening out.

S9E13.title: The One Where Chandler Takes a Bath
S9E13.des:
As Joey agonizes over his secret affection for
                Rachel, Monica mistakenly thinks that he is infatuated with Phoebe.

S9E14.title: The One with the Secret Closet
S9E14.des:
Joey realizes that his feelings for Rachel are
                excluding Ross from the joys of impending fatherhood. Chandler is obsessed with Monica's locked
                closet.

S9E15.title: The One with the Birthing Video
S9E15.des:
Monica prepares a special Valentine's Day for
                Chandler, who is too shocked to respond favorably after accidentally viewing the wrong videotape.

S9E16.title: The One Where Joey Tells Rachel
S9E16.des:
Guilt-ridden Joey confesses his love for Rachel
                to the flabbergasted Ross. Phoebe's new boyfriend shares numerous personality traits with Monica.

S9E17.title: The One with the Tea Leaves
S9E17.des:
Feeling awkward after revealing his feelings to
                Rachel, Joey avoids contact with her. Phoebe believes she will soon meet the man of her dreams.

S9E18.title: The One in Massapequa
S9E18.des:
Monica must give a toast at a 35th wedding
                anniversary party for her parents. Jack and Judy ask Ross and Rachel to pretend to be married at the
                party.

S9E19.title: The One with Joey's Interview
S9E19.des:
Joey is thrilled when his name is used in a Soap
                Opera Digest crossword puzzle, yet he is reluctant to let the magazine do a profile about him.

S9E20.title: The One with the Baby Shower
S9E20.des:
Rachel panics during a party in anticipation of
                her baby's birth when she realizes how unprepared she is to care for an infant.

S9E21.title: The One with the Cooking Class
S9E21.des:
Monica tries to sway a food critic's opinion.
                Nervous about a major job interview, Chandler receives some questionable coaching from Phoebe.

S9E22.title: The One Where Rachel Is Late
S9E22.des:
When Rachel's pregnancy goes beyond her
                projected delivery date, the pain makes Rachel increasingly irritable.

S9E23.title: The One Where Rachel Has a Baby: Part 1
S9E23.des:
Rachel waits in the hospital maternity ward with
                Ross, as numerous other pregnant women are wheeled in while Rachel's painful labor continues.

S9E24.title: The One Where Rachel Has a Baby: Part 2
S9E24.des:
Rachel gives birth to a beautiful girl, and Ross
                kisses Rachel. Both hiding their feelings, they wonder how to proceed.

year:
Rachel is pregnant and faces single parenthood, while
            Joey agonizes over his feelings for her. Chandler and Monica are now dealing with married life.
about:
Rachel is pregnant and faces single parenthood, while
            Joey agonizes over his feelings for her. Chandler and Monica are now dealing with married life.
